data.description: Whether this is your first home, or you are right sizing. Move-in ready, all brick home on peaceful tree lined street, directly  across from Rathje Park, complete with green space, playground, preschool, baseball field and pond. Bright and airy with  hardwood floors throughout first floor. Home painted in neutral colors to match any decor. Open living room/ dining room.  Eat-in kitchen with quartz counter tops, tile floor and newer appliances. Three bedrooms with ample closet space. Partially  finished basement. Walk in cedar closet. Nice sized yard with cement patio, retractable awning, a built-in gas grill, and great  neighbors make the outdoor space a place to enjoy. Highly desirable walk to Metra, Prairie Path, school, and downtown  Wheaton location.
